{"tid":2112739,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「收成波」埋怨《蘋果》日日鬧 堅稱百萬計中產有共鳴","createTime":"2020-07-17T14:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T15:20:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2eff2dfebdc7c165e1c73f8db4dcb2514b54181e","tid":2112739,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200717/AEBWCD6ZDDJNBKTFKPJ5DMZ6BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FAEBWCD6ZDDJNBKTFKPJ5DMZ6BA%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpeExUl64GHAvDQsppiVFus8%3D&h=15899782\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FAEBWCD6ZDDJNBKTFKPJ5DMZ6BA%2F&h=7e906a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200717/AEBWCD6ZDDJNBKTFKPJ5DMZ6BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n財務委員會今日（17日）完成本年度、亦是本屆立法會內最後一次會議。主席陳健波在年結記者會表示，本年度共舉行了56次、共253小時的會議，通過85項、涉及4,464億元撥款，大幅高於上年度的1,221億元，創7年新高。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波又趁機批評《蘋果》多次引述他的「收成期」論，指「特別係《蘋果日報》，日日都有專欄鬧我講收成期呢樣嘢」，強調有數以百萬計的中產及中年人士均對他的言論有共鳴。"},{"pid":"e14a3be135dc8a742540c1cd580c95e61b280642","tid":2112739,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61be85361b8f83d37b8062ed42b2a0fabcd54d3","tid":2112739,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6d126f2a740d96e36317206999f86d222be951","tid":2112739,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14a3be135dc8a742540c1cd580c95e61b280642","tid":2